thread.title: Naomi

author: Naomi
title: Naomi
text: The product was high quality and very useful. I found the shipping process confusing- notshipping information (tracking number, confirmation of shipment) was sent so I was unsure when the product would arrive however customer service was able to provide some details when I contacted them via Facebook. I would recommend this product to others and order from them again.
